    <div class="banner">Multi-Intent Resolution Flow</div>

    <div class="scenario">
      <h3>Scenario</h3>
      <p>
        A Target customer calls about their <strong>Target Circle Card</strong>. They first request a balance inquiry, then report a <strong>fraudulent charge</strong>.
        The Genesys Cloud <strong>Virtual Agent</strong> expresses empathy, walks through verification steps, and offers to cancel the card and send a replacement.
        When the customer requests expedited shipping due to upcoming <strong>Black Friday</strong>, the Virtual Agent escalates to a live Target agent.
        Genesys <strong>Agent Copilot</strong> summarizes the interaction and assists the agent with <strong>Knowledge Articles</strong>, <strong>Next Best Action</strong> recommendations,
        and <strong>Disposition</strong> suggestions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <section class="flow">
      <h2>Flow 1: Virtual Agent Interaction</h2>
      <div class="step-grid">
        <div class="step"><strong>Customer Call</strong><p>Customer calls Target support line via voice channel.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Virtual Agent Greeting</strong><p>Genesys Cloud Virtual Agent greets and identifies the customer.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Balance Request</strong><p>Customer asks for Target Circle Card balance; VA retrieves and reads back balance.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Fraud Concern</strong><p>Customer reports a fraudulent charge; VA expresses empathy and explains verification steps.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Cancellation Offer</strong><p>VA offers to cancel card and send replacement; customer accepts.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Expedite Request</strong><p>Customer requests expedited delivery before Black Friday.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Escalation Trigger</strong><p>VA escalates to live Target agent for further handling.</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="snake-line horizontal flow1a"></div>
      <div class="snake-line vertical flow1b"></div>
      <div class="snake-line horizontal flow1c"></div>
      <div class="arrowhead end1"></div>
      <div class="arrowhead end2"></div>
    </section>

    <section class="flow">
      <h2>Flow 2: Live Agent & Copilot Experience</h2>
      <div class="step-grid">
        <div class="step"><strong>Agent Handoff</strong><p>Genesys Agent Copilot summarizes the conversation for the Target agent.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Contextual Guidance</strong><p>Copilot surfaces Knowledge Articles, Next Best Actions, and Agent Checklists in real time.</p></div>
        <div class="step"><strong>Disposition Suggestion</strong><p>Post-call, Copilot recommends the best Disposition to classify the interaction.</p></div>
      </div>
    </section>

